Package: libseatuya0
Architecture: any
Multi-Arch: same
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: C wrapper library for tuyapp Tuya device communication
 seatuya is a C wrapper library for tuyapp, providing a pure C API for
 local Tuya smart-device communication.  Supports protocol versions 3.1,
 3.3, 3.4, and 3.5.

Package: libseatuya-dev
Section: libdevel
Architecture: any
Multi-Arch: same
Depends: libseatuya0 (= ${binary:Version}),
         libssl-dev,
         ${misc:Depends}
Description: Development files for libseatuya
 seatuya is a C wrapper library for tuyapp, providing a pure C API for
 local Tuya smart-device communication.
 .
 This package contains the header files, development symlinks, and
 manpage needed for building programs that use libseatuya.
